	<body id = 'pagebody'><p>Apple's 10 a.m. PDT event will be streamed to a handful of OS/browser combinations. Is there anyplace on Ask Different where people will discuss things both live and after the event?</p>

<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.apple.com/apple-events/march-2016/" rel="nofollow">http://www.apple.com/apple-events/march-2016/</a></li>
